social_posts.post_text: Sweet Zeus… I am so happy you found your forever home! @spcatexas
This sweet guy knows my love language!! @oakmeadowranch_texas
Happy New Year! @revmichaelrowan

Almost four years… that’s how long Apollo has been waiting for his forever family.
 
We don’t know why. He doesn’t know why. He’s non-destructive, house trained, and would do best in a home with no young children or other fur babies. Apollo is a chill couch potato who just wants to cuddle with his people. 
 
Please share and help Apollo get adopted. Or contact us to meet him!
 
Find more information about Apollo here:  https://spca.org/adoptable/apollo/

11 Years. 4015 days. 96360 hours. 5781600 minutes. 346896000 seconds. I wouldn’t trade one of those seconds to not be married to you. You are my best friend, my whole heart, my boo, my swole mate, my partner, my everything. The amount of growth we have achieved in these 11 years is nothing short of miraculous. God is our strength and firm foundation. When marriages have crumbled all around us, we have stood together. We have weathered the storms of life, loved hard, forgiven freely, laughed hard, and God has been our strength. I love you. I love you without fail. I love you forever. Thank you for choosing me, for loving me, for providing and protecting me. Happy Anniversary baby! @revmichaelrowan

Sweet Zeus. The way you look so happy all the time. You cuddle me, beg for treats, and stay right by my side. I promise! I will be your advocate until you find your home! @spcatexas #rescue #adopt #zeus
Happy Valentines Day to my best friend and handsome hubby! You’re what I want and need! Your everything to me! Now let’s go crush leg day! ❤️ @revmichaelrowan
My sweet Zeus found his home! I think this one is gonna stick! They loved him and he gets kids again! One on the way too! I will miss his sweet face but he is finally home! @spcatexas
I love working for the @spcatexas! Making donation deliveries to other local shelters helps spread the generosity of the donations we get! #getandgive #givebacktothecommunity
This happy boy Zeus is still waiting for his forever home at  @spcatexas ! He gets so happy for his treats! #Give2PetsNTX

At home leg workout! All you need is a set of dumbbells, a weighted medicine ball and a booty band. 

Superset:
30 sec- High knee ball taps
12- Front load squats
12-RDL
12-Weighted jump squats
12-Sumo squats
12-Lateral lunges (each leg)
30 sec- Booty band squat walks 
12- Kick backs (each leg)

Repeat superset 5 rounds!
